title: Medieval Mistletoe - One Magical Christmas Season
description:
Four Christmas novellas from Four best selling Medieval authors

Mistletoe Magic by Laurel O'Donnell A confident knight arrives home to find his childhood friend grown into much more then he remembered. The lady of the castle keeps a dangerous secret that threatens all she holds dear. Will Mistletoe Magic save them? 

Perfect Poison by Denise Domning Injured in body and soul, the lord of Freyne is reluctantly swept into the Yuletide festivities only to find redemption in the arms of the woman he spurned. 

Wild Highland Mistletoe by Eliza Knight A daring rescue attempt just before the holiday season threatens not only Magnus' and Arbella's love, but their very lives. 

One Knight under the Mistletoe by Catherine Kean Seven years earlier a young lord played a trick upon a reluctant lady and she has never forgotten the humiliation of that moment. As dangerous secrets come to light, will she put the past behind her and accept his love?
